uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.gui
Class DisplayPhylogenyFactory

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.gui.DisplayPhylogenyFactory

public class DisplayPhylogenyFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This is a factory object: the the factory methods are called in static context to create an array of DisplayPhylogeny objects from DisplayPhylogenyFactory#fromFile(), DisplayPhylogenyFactory#fromTreeNode(), DisplayPhylogenyFactory#fromNewickTreeRepresentation(), and DisplayPhylogenyFactory#fromString() inputs.

Author:
Joe Parker, Kitson Consulting / Queen Mary University of London
